	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just kinda want to know where you get your statistics from and who as verified them.<br><br>1, There are either rogues or monks in more than 1 in 10 groups, however neither of these classes have taunt and rogues have evade, so this should even up the agro<br><br>2, Unfortunately very true.&nbsp;&nbsp;Agro is something that needs to be managed, learn to manage agro and your main tank will keep it.  If you dont understand agro then mobs can ping pong and thats when peeps start taking trips to bind points.<br><br>3, The low damage fast weapons that are rated so highly tend to be ones with good ratios.  keeping in mind that weilding 2 9/18s has the potential be equivilent to weilding 1 18/18 it is very hard not to rate these weapons highly.  Especially at higher levels where my Warrior at lvl52 hits regularly for 50+ damage with a 11 damage weapon.<br><br>4, 5 times out of 10 maybe? or perhaps this trend is changing, cos there are more and more peeps out there with nice stompy 2 handers these days.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
